<%= provide :title, 'Reports' %>
<div class="container">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="project-margin-column"></div>
    <div class="project">
      <h1>Data acquisition report server</h1>

      <p>
        In modern enterprise level building objects there is a need to monitor status and collect data from up to hundreds of medium meters.
        This includes electrical energy, water consumption, heat, etc.. This project solves problem of storing periodical medium usage data from
        meters and presenting it in convenient form to the end user.
      </p>

      <p>It features:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Tabelar, circular, column and more report types.</li>
        <li>User can filter data by various scopes (meter description, serial number, localization, etc.).</li>
        <li>User can see meter usage for any period.</li>
        <li>User can check health/online status for every meter.</li>
        <li>User can export every report to pdf or xls files, so he can handle it to building tenant to show him his periodical medium usage.</li>
      </ul>

      <p>This type of projects involved on my part:
        <ul>

          <li>
            Integrating <%= link_to 'Schneider StruxureWare Building Operation', 'http://www.schneider-electric.com/b2b/en/solutions/enterprise-solutions/solutions/enterprise-software-suites-building-operation/', target: '_blank' %>
            with <%= link_to 'Microsoft reporting services (SSRS)', 'https://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/library/ms157231.aspx', target: '_blank' %>.
          </li>

          <li>
            Creating reports using <%= link_to 'Microsoft Report Builder', 'https://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/library/dd220460.aspx', target: '_blank' %> software.
          </li>

          <li>
            Creating set of custom T-SQL proocedures intended to extract periodical meter medium usage along with additional info like serial number or description.
            Example can be found <%= link_to 'here', 'https://gist.github.com/KamilMilewski/159818632a5707471b76a3dac15edeb2', target: '_blank' %>.
          </li>

          <li>
            Integrating <%= link_to 'M-Bus', 'http://www.m-bus.com/info/mbuse.php', target: '_blank' %>/<%= link_to 'Modbus', 'http://www.simplymodbus.ca/FAQ.htm#Modbus', target: '_blank' %>
            gateway controllers with
            <%= link_to 'Schneider StruxureWare Building Operation', 'http://www.schneider-electric.com/b2b/en/solutions/enterprise-solutions/solutions/enterprise-software-suites-building-operation/', target: '_blank' %>
            software.
          </li>

        </ul>
      </p>

      <p>I implemented this system for:
        <ul>

          <li><%= link_to 'The International Conference Centre', 'http://www.mck.katowice.eu/en', target: '_blank' %> in Katowice.</li>

          <li><%= link_to 'PRIME Corporate Center in Warsaw', 'http://primecorporatecenter.pl/en', target: '_blank' %> in Warsaw.</li>

          <li><%= link_to 'Galeria Jurowiecka', 'http://galeriajurowiecka.com.pl/', target: '_blank' %> in Bia≈Çystok.</li>

        </ul>
      </p>

